		optRxId OBJECT-TYPE
			SYNTAX INTEGER (1..16)
			ACCESS read-only
			STATUS mandatory
			DESCRIPTION
				"Second index to the table. If the module contains only one 
				functional entity, optRxId 1 is used. With more functional 
				entities, each of them is numbered with a unique opRxId (eg.
				multiple optical receivers in a module).
				
				The optRxIdshould should be identical to the function 
				entity indexes used in the HMS-HE-MIBs (eg.heOpRxInputIndex, 
				heOpRxOutputIndex etc.).
				"
			::= { optRxModuleEntry 1 }

		
